Automated:

F1 on slot extraction (dates, budget, party size) against labeled chats.

Recall@K for POI retrieval vs. curated lists.

Constraint satisfaction rate (open hours, travel time limits).

Human:

5‑point rubrics: suitability to preferences, logical flow, pacing, novelty.

A/B prompts and ranking weights.

Success Gate:

≥80% constraint satisfaction; average human score ≥4/5 across 20 test users.
